            </item>
        
            <item>
                <title>Installing Fritzing easily on Ubuntu</title>
                <description>&lt;p&gt;This is an easy method to install Fritzing on Ubuntu using packages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Run in a terminal &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;sudo apt install fritzing fritzing-parts&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can now open Fritzing.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2019 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
